text: Constanţa is the largest Romanian seaport on the Black Sea. It is the largest city in Dobruja. It is also the capital of Constanţa County and one of the biggest cities in Romania. == Other websites == * Official administration site * Constanţa Seaport official site * Map * Map Category:County capitals of Romania Category:Municipalities of Romania Category:Cities in Romania Category:Port cities and towns of the Black Sea Category:Constanța County
